  "detailed_description": "KnightMan is a 2D pixel art action platformer with retro style graphics. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/dcb759a28570955bce3264ea3090f9d1.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/dcb759a28570955bce3264ea3090f9d1.webm?t=1692601548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/97e046e0d697be0c806f570cae101c8e.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" width=192 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/97e046e0d697be0c806f570cae101c8e.webm?t=1692601548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/a4e21345fb53faa9c6c505a39484c8ed.apng?t=1692601548\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/a4e21345fb53faa9c6c505a39484c8ed.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span><br><br>Play as KnightMan. Fight and jump your way through 20 levels across 5 unique zones, each populated with different enemies and traps. Defeat bosses, save maidens and collect coins to purchase weapons, powers and trinkets to help you along your journey to defeat the corrupted Elven Lord.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/7fdac2864f813c073dbc417b9f3de992.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/7fdac2864f813c073dbc417b9f3de992.webm?t=1692601548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/f561393c837f6d94d16766731806b901.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/f561393c837f6d94d16766731806b901.webm?t=1692601548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/ffca6c14831780d89993e2841a9f708c.apng?t=1692601548\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/ffca6c14831780d89993e2841a9f708c.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br>- Traverse a variety of hand crafted levels.<br><br>- 2 Playable Characters with unique play styles, KnightMan and RogueElf<br><br>- 5 unique Zones each with their own aesthetic and enemy types. <br><br>- Find Fire, Ice and Lightening powerups in each level that grant KnightMan different attacks, <br><br>- Purchase powerful upgrades, weapons and trinkets.<br><br>- Fight powerful bosses.<br><br>- Save beautiful maidens who will reward you handsomely.<br><br>- Bonus Boss Rush mode!<br><br>KNIGHTMAN!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508070/extras/5cbcdd3cea0f59f0c89eea6d95590df5.poster.avif?t=1692601548\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2